## Wave Proposal Guidelines
- Each Wave should be completable in a single work session
- Wave 1 has no prerequisites (can be started immediately)
- Wave 2 and later may depend on Wave 1 completion
- Each Wave must include concrete actions (add DoD, add dependencies, add labels, etc.)

## Action Types
- `add_dod`: Append DoD items to the Issue description
- `add_dependency`: Set dependencies between Issues
- `add_label`: Add a label to an Issue
- `update_description`: Update an Issue description
- `create`: Create a new sub-issue under a parent Issue
- `cancel`: Cancel an Issue (Backlog/Todo status only). Requires reason in detail field.

